00:23:08.050 --> 00:23:09.440
I mean...

00:23:10.410 --> 00:23:11.980
what's this?

00:23:19.890 --> 00:23:21.550
You were secretly drawing me?

00:23:25.290 --> 00:23:26.160
Just doodling.

00:23:28.090 --> 00:23:29.490
Just doodling?

00:23:33.960 --> 00:23:35.200
Well, I'm right here.

00:23:35.330 --> 00:23:36.730
You can draw me properly.

00:23:39.640 --> 00:23:40.640
I'm done drawing.

00:23:40.641 --> 00:23:49.545
(Watch on www.dramacool.club Support Admin)

00:23:41.570 --> 00:23:42.530
Why?

