Keep drawing. I want you to draw me.

00:24:51.680 --> 00:24:53.910
[Pet Home]

00:24:57.700 --> 00:24:58.330
Here.

00:25:03.500 --> 00:25:04.480
Wait, who are you?

00:25:04.480 --> 00:25:05.000
Help!

00:25:05.000 --> 00:25:06.930
Wait! You've got the wrong person.
Come on!

00:25:06.930 --> 00:25:07.540
Wait!

00:25:22.520 --> 00:25:23.700
Just pay back the money for him.

00:25:23.700 --> 00:25:25.290
It's only natural
that a son repays his father's debt.

00:25:25.290 --> 00:25:27.160
Come on.
He owes you money, so go after him.

00:25:27.160 --> 00:25:28.160
Don't go after me!

00:25:50.820 --> 00:25:52.480
How could you drive like that?

00:26:19.860 --> 00:26:20.790
Why are you here?

00:26:21.220 --> 00:26:21.810
Let's go.

00:26:26.600 --> 00:26:27.910
That's all for today's class.

00:26:27.910 --> 00:26:28.910
Class dismissed.

00:26:28.920 --> 00:26:30.850
Come on. Let's go play basketball.

00:26:31.040 --> 00:26:32.640
Wait for me, I'll go with you.

00:26:38.140 --> 00:26:38.750
Let's go!

00:26:40.960 --> 00:26:41.850
Wait for me!

00:26:50.530 --> 00:26:51.570
Pass it to me!

00:26:53.440 --> 00:26:54.530
Over here! To me!

00:27:00.210 --> 00:27:01.050
Pass it to me!

00:27:19.210 --> 00:27:20.210
Where's your dad?

00:27:21.960 --> 00:27:22.890
I don't know.

00:27:23.090 --> 00:27:23.950
You don't know?

00:27:25.080 --> 00:27:26.760
You're his son and you don't know?

00:27:26.760 --> 00:27:28.440
I haven't seen him for a long time either.

00:27:28.440 --> 00:27:29.360
Haven't seen him?

00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:30.090
Pull him up!

00:27:32.440 --> 00:27:33.370
Let me tell you.

00:27:34.050 --> 00:27:35.720
Your dad owes me a lot of money.

00:27:35.850 --> 00:27:37.160
If he can't pay it back, you will.

00:27:37.160 --> 00:27:38.640
I really don't know where he is.

00:27:38.640 --> 00:27:40.050
Don't think that if you don't tell me,

00:27:40.050 --> 00:27:41.910
I won't find out where your dad is.

00:27:43.660 --> 00:27:44.720
What are you doing?

00:27:46.470 --> 00:27:48.000
Let's go!

00:27:48.330 --> 00:27:49.590
After them! Don't run!

00:27:51.890 --> 00:27:53.100
Hurry! After them!

00:27:54.090 --> 00:27:54.890
Stop running!

00:27:55.610 --> 00:27:57.010
You brats! Stop running!

00:27:59.090 --> 00:28:00.090
Stop right there!

00:28:13.960 --> 00:28:14.680
Thanks.

00:28:17.310 --> 00:28:18.770
I've always wanted to ask—

00:28:20.110 --> 00:28:22.240
why are your shoelaces always untied?

00:28:22.240 --> 00:28:24.640
I'm afraid that if I squat down
and tie them,

00:28:24.720 --> 00:28:25.980
no one will wait for me.

00:28:26.330 --> 00:28:28.640
I want to stay with everyone.
I don't want to fall behind.

00:28:28.640 --> 00:28:29.840
So I've gotten used to

00:28:29.890 --> 00:28:31.690
whether my laces are tied or not.

00:28:42.320 --> 00:28:44.030
If your shoelaces come undone,

00:28:44.030 --> 00:28:45.030
you must fix them.

00:28:46.120 --> 00:28:46.850
Don't worry.

00:28:47.200 --> 00:28:48.200
I'll wait for you.

00:28:48.690 --> 00:28:49.360
Okay.

00:29:07.940 --> 00:29:09.800
Who did you get into trouble with?

00:29:12.570 --> 00:29:13.640
It's my dad.

00:29:14.240 --> 00:29:16.640
I don't know
who he's messed with this time.

00:29:19.290 --> 00:29:20.160
Who are they?

00:29:23.890 --> 00:29:26.490
Not many people in Manshi
would lend him money.

00:29:26.960 --> 00:29:28.960
Just ask around and you'll find out.

00:29:33.570 --> 00:29:34.920
Let's get your dad out first.

00:29:34.920 --> 00:29:36.320
I'll help with the money.

00:29:36.540 --> 00:29:37.670
How much do you need?

00:29:41.290 --> 00:29:42.770
My shop's making money.

00:29:43.060 --> 00:29:43.920
Don't worry about the money.

00:29:43.920 --> 00:29:45.120
Just tell me how much.

00:29:49.050 --> 00:29:50.650
Having a brother like you...

00:29:51.960 --> 00:29:52.620
is worth it.

00:29:55.600 --> 00:29:56.400
Brandy.

00:30:00.350 --> 00:30:02.410
I can't keep going like this anymore.

00:30:07.740 --> 00:30:08.820
In the future,

00:30:09.430 --> 00:30:10.960
I want to open a small diner,

00:30:11.410 --> 00:30:12.610
adopt two stray dogs,

00:30:13.860 --> 00:30:16.260
and just chat with you for fun
when I'm free.

00:30:17.590 --> 00:30:18.650
That would be nice.

00:30:25.730 --> 00:30:27.330
Let's raise the money first.

00:30:34.480 --> 00:30:36.420
[Pet Home]

00:31:06.000 --> 00:31:07.200
It's not enough.

00:31:07.850 --> 00:31:09.710
I'm still short. What should I do?

00:31:22.540 --> 00:31:23.300
Sanlai!

00:31:28.350 --> 00:31:29.070
Sanlai!

00:31:34.060 --> 00:31:35.590
What are you doing, Sanlai?

00:31:40.110 --> 00:31:41.530
[Brandy, I went to pick up my dad.
Don't worry about me.]

00:32:03.480 --> 00:32:04.240
Officer Lu,

00:32:05.020 --> 00:32:06.200
my friend is in danger.

00:32:06.200 --> 00:32:07.860
I need police assistance now.

00:32:08.060 --> 00:32:08.670
Yes.

00:32:09.070 --> 00:32:10.220
I'll send you his phone number.

00:32:10.220 --> 00:32:12.620
Please check his location
and send it to me.

00:32:12.640 --> 00:32:13.240
Okay.

00:32:13.490 --> 00:32:15.020
I'll wait for your message.

00:32:33.090 --> 00:32:34.020
Place your bets!

00:32:35.160 --> 00:32:36.850
Alright. Let's go.

00:32:52.150 --> 00:32:53.410
You dare show up again?

00:32:55.210 --> 00:32:56.250
Cut the crap.

00:32:58.240 --> 00:32:59.770
I've brought you the money.

00:33:00.070 --> 00:33:00.730
Where is he?

00:33:11.740 --> 00:33:13.370
Who told you to come?

00:33:14.030 --> 00:33:15.490
You think I want to be here?

00:33:16.400 --> 00:33:17.790
Alright. You've seen him.

00:33:17.790 --> 00:33:18.390
The money.

00:33:35.780 --> 00:33:36.650
Don't push me.

00:33:37.960 --> 00:33:39.040
You've got some nerve.

00:33:39.040 --> 00:33:40.070
Let him go!

00:33:41.440 --> 00:33:42.320
Do you even know how to use a knife?

00:33:42.320 --> 00:33:43.610
Come on. Here.

00:33:43.640 --> 00:33:44.710
Run, Lai Qide!

00:33:46.540 --> 00:33:48.430
Don't hit my son! Don't hit my son!

00:33:48.750 --> 00:33:49.750
Stop hitting him!

00:33:51.370 --> 00:33:52.020
Alright.

00:33:52.270 --> 00:33:53.270
Stop hitting him.

00:34:20.030 --> 00:34:20.750
Stop!

00:34:21.440 --> 00:34:22.250
You're quite a fighter.

00:34:22.250 --> 00:34:23.739
Let's see what's faster,
your fist or my knife.

00:34:23.739 --> 00:34:24.489
Kill him!

00:34:27.900 --> 00:34:28.750
Brandy!

00:34:42.370 --> 00:34:43.260
Lai Qide.

00:34:44.340 --> 00:34:46.290
Tell me what you really want.

00:34:47.320 --> 00:34:48.650
You gambled away our house.

00:34:48.650 --> 00:34:50.120
We lost my mom, our home, everything!

00:34:50.120 --> 00:34:51.190
Tell me why!

00:34:51.210 --> 00:34:53.210
Why are you so addicted to gambling?

00:34:56.230 --> 00:34:57.470
I'm not...

00:34:57.620 --> 00:34:59.450
Don't give me any excuses.

00:34:59.850 --> 00:35:01.980
Don't cry in front of me. It's useless.

00:35:04.610 --> 00:35:05.810
This is the last time.

00:35:13.820 --> 00:35:14.420
Let's go.

00:35:39.880 --> 00:35:41.600
Are you really going to
just leave your dad there

00:35:41.600 --> 00:35:42.400
and let him be?

00:35:52.040 --> 00:35:53.640
My dad is really getting old.

00:35:55.440 --> 00:35:58.770
I scolded him like that just now
and he didn't even talk back.

00:35:59.600 --> 00:36:02.400
I don't know when it started,
but he even cries now.

00:36:07.260 --> 00:36:09.190
Do you think I went too far just now?

00:36:17.080 --> 00:36:18.940
Come on. What are you laughing at?

00:36:20.190 --> 00:36:22.500
What's wrong with you? What's so funny?

00:36:22.940 --> 00:36:25.070
The way you were hopping mad back there

00:36:25.450 --> 00:36:27.110
looked exactly like a monkey.

00:36:28.850 --> 00:36:30.220
You've got the nerve to say that about me?

00:36:30.220 --> 00:36:31.260
Look at your face.

00:36:34.370 --> 00:36:35.080
Alright.

00:36:35.530 --> 00:36:36.570
Stop being dramatic.

00:36:36.570 --> 00:36:37.290
Go.

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:46.130
You told me to go.

00:37:07.260 --> 00:37:08.190
Are you alright?

00:37:27.690 --> 00:37:28.890
It's specially made.

00:37:29.460 --> 00:37:31.460
Put this phone against his

00:37:31.690 --> 00:37:33.220
and it'll install a Trojan.

00:37:44.270 --> 00:37:47.420
[Speeding Auto House]

00:37:53.630 --> 00:37:55.500
Why are you putting it in this car?

00:37:55.880 --> 00:37:58.810
My car's going to race,
so I need to reduce its weight.

00:38:02.680 --> 00:38:04.720
Hello, your delivery.

00:38:06.650 --> 00:38:07.480
Coming.

00:38:10.250 --> 00:38:11.120
Thank you.

00:38:14.560 --> 00:38:15.560
Please sign here.

00:38:17.690 --> 00:38:18.440
Thanks.

00:38:18.520 --> 00:38:19.080
Okay.

00:38:26.080 --> 00:38:26.850
What's this?

00:38:27.410 --> 00:38:29.010
You'll know when you open it.

00:38:50.530 --> 00:38:51.370
Do you like it?

00:38:53.580 --> 00:38:55.980
Do you know
how hard this is to put together?

00:38:58.330 --> 00:39:00.660
I seriously think you're messing with me.

00:39:01.020 --> 00:39:02.820
I didn't say you have to do it now.

00:39:03.120 --> 00:39:05.250
We've got plenty of time in the future.

00:39:05.770 --> 00:39:06.650
One day,

00:39:06.920 --> 00:39:08.000
we can finish

00:39:08.000 --> 00:39:09.850
this great project together.

00:39:20.990 --> 00:39:22.590
You want to finish half of it?

00:39:25.120 --> 00:39:26.890
Oh my goodness, Lightning!

00:39:27.450 --> 00:39:29.660
Did you roll in the mud? You're filthy.

00:39:30.200 --> 00:39:30.950
Yeah.

00:39:31.730 --> 00:39:32.680
Why are you so dirty?

00:39:32.680 --> 00:39:35.240
What should we do?
Puppies can't take a bath.

00:39:36.050 --> 00:39:38.530
Well...
we should at least clean it up a bit.

00:39:42.720 --> 00:39:44.320
Lightning, drink some milk.

00:39:47.670 --> 00:39:48.790
It's my dog.

00:39:49.250 --> 00:39:50.900
Why does it listen to you more than to me?

00:39:50.900 --> 00:39:52.630
You're even jealous over a dog?

00:39:55.240 --> 00:39:56.760
Lightning,

00:39:56.850 --> 00:39:58.810
if Mom and Dad split up one day,

00:39:58.920 --> 00:40:01.130
would you go with Dad or Mom?

00:40:01.650 --> 00:40:03.040
Are you going to ask next

00:40:03.210 --> 00:40:05.000
whether he'd save Zhao or Mu first

00:40:05.000 --> 00:40:06.800
if they both fell into the water?

00:40:07.480 --> 00:40:08.730
Dogs can't really swim.

00:40:08.730 --> 00:40:09.990
They only dog‑paddle.

00:40:10.030 --> 00:40:12.200
Zhao and Mu can both swim.

00:40:24.530 --> 00:40:25.180
Mu.

00:40:27.140 --> 00:40:28.470
Go change your clothes.

00:40:29.920 --> 00:40:31.180
I'll leave this to you.

00:40:32.920 --> 00:40:33.850
My dress...

00:40:39.520 --> 00:40:40.850
Which one should I wear?

00:40:42.150 --> 00:40:43.350
I'll find one for you.

00:40:56.970 --> 00:40:59.030
Help me see which one looks good on me.

00:41:04.870 --> 00:41:06.890
Do you think anything
would look good on me

00:41:06.890 --> 00:41:07.890
with my figure?

00:41:13.300 --> 00:41:14.010
Mu.

00:41:15.140 --> 00:41:15.820
What is it?